org.mitre.mat.core
Class Annotation

java.lang.Object
  org.mitre.mat.core.AnnotationCore
      org.mitre.mat.core.Annotation

public class Annotation
extends AnnotationCore

The core object that corresponds to a span annotation. The attribute values are a sequence of Objects, which pair up with the attributes in the attribute List.
